    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Scaled floor plans showing HVAC layout, which is the layout for heating, ventilation, and air contitioning. They may include small drawings of an adjacent elevation. For other drawings of HVAC systems, use "HVAC drawings."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000048485/Stamper and Koral, Handbook of Air Conditioning, Heating, and Ventilating (1979)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Se refiere a planos de piso a escala que muestran el despliegue del HVAC, que corresponde al despliegue de la calefacción, ventilación y aire acondicionado. También puede incluir pequeños dibujos de una elevación adjacente. Para otros dibujos de sistemas de HVAC, use "dibujo de HVAC".</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wordt gebruikt voor grondtekeningen op schaal van een W-systeem; hieronder kunnen ook aanverwante kleine aanzichtschetsen vallen. Gebruik 'W-tekeningen' voor andere tekeningen van W-systemen.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052409/Vliet, De Architectengroep (z.j.)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>按比例呈現中央空調管道配置的平面圖即暖氣、通風及空調之配置。有時亦包括小型立面圖。至於其他中央空調系統的繪圖，則使用「中央空調圖」一詞。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000079740/AS-Academia Sinica data (2014-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Plantas de pisos em escala que mostram o leiaute de aquecimento, ventilação e ar-condicionado. Podem incluir desenhos pequenos de uma elevação adjacente. Para outros desenhos dos sistemas de ventilação e calefação, use "desenhos de climatização".</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Portuguese</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000179/VP-intern</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000110648/Portuguese Translation Intern Project (2020-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
